wikipedia_page.main: Lady Alice Louisa Lilly Manners (born 27 April 1995) is an English columnist, fashion model, and socialite.

response: In 2020, Ferry was reported to be the long-term boyfriend of Lady Alice Manners, a daughter of the Duke of Rutland, and to be living with her at Belvoir Castle.Hilary Rose, "A 356-room castle, three socialites, no staff…", The Times, 14 May 2020, accessed 6 December 2021
